ing%20cars%20to%20Nashville%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20part%20by%20making%20its%20service%20available%20on%20the%20Lyft%20platform.%20The%20partnership%20means%20Waymo%20is%20now%20partnered%20with%20two%20of%20the%20biggest%20ride-hailing%20companies%20in%20North%20America%3A%20Uber%20and%20Lyft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20smaller%20scale%2C%20Waymo%20said%20today%20that%20it%20will%20make%20its%20existing%20robotaxi%20fleet%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-one-driverless-car-service-launches-in-phoenix-arizona-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMetro-Phoenix%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0available%20to%20Chandler%20Flex%20riders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChandler%20Flex%20is%20an%20on-demand%20microtransit%20program%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvia-ceo-wants-to-take-transportation-company-public-uber-lyft-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epowered%20by%20Via%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20New%20York%20City-based%20public%20transit%20software%20company%20that%20went%20public%20earlier%20this%20week.%20The%20program%20operates%20similarly%20to%20an%20Uber%20or%20Lyft%20but%20has%20lower%20fares%20and%20determines%20routes%20based%20on%20where%20other%20riders%20are%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChandler%20Flex's%20ridership%20is%20small%20compared%20to%20Waymo's%20monthly%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20120%2C000%20rides%20in%203%20years%20compared%20to%20Waymo's%20more%20than%20250%2C000%20trips%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20just%20goes%20to%20show%20how%20a%20company%20backed%20by%20a%20tech%20titan%20is%20willing%20to%20try%20different%20avenues%2C%20small%20or%20large%2C%20to%20get%20more%20riders%20in%20robotaxi%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20purpose%20of%20what%20Waymo%20does%20today%2C%20I%20think%2C%20is%20to%20learn%2C%26quot%3B%20Brad%20Templeton%2C%20who%20was%20a%20consultant%20for%20Waymo's%20Google%20Self-Driving%20Car%20Project%20phase%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BUp%20un