%3BUltimately%2C%20this%20partnership%20was%20created%20to%20help%20fill%20gaps%20in%20transportation%20and%20create%20even%20greater%20access%20to%20affordable%20microtransit%20in%20a%20community%20we%20already%20operate%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETempleton%2C%20however%2C%20still%20sees%20the%20move%20as%20an%20early%20glimpse%20into%20a%20future%20where%20autonomous%20vehicles%20could%20replace%20some%20of%20the%20costly%20aspects%20of%20maintaining%20a%20public%20transit%20system%2C%20including%20the%20fuel%20for%20buses%20and%20the%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPractical%20people%20have%20already%20been%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20microtransits%20because%20they%20know%20that%20the%20(transit)%20systems%20they%20operate%20today%20are%20very%20inefficient%20and%20very%20expensive%20and%20that%20it's%20actually%20cheaper%20to%20do%20it%20with%20smaller%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20kind%20of%20been%20expecting%20experiments%20in%20this%20sooner%20than%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-business-strategy-partnerships-uber-lyft-via-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758195901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cb650757d362d375e861f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-business-strategy-partnerships-uber-lyft-via-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Waymo%20is%20using%20partnerships%20with%20ride-hailing%20giants%20like%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20as%20one%20strategy%20to%20get%20more%20riders%20inside%20its%20robotaxis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-business-strategy-partnerships-uber-lyft-via-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUr