ions-for-staying-amid-second-bankruptcy-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpirit%20Airlines%20bosses%3C%2Fa%3E%20want%20to%20cut%20pilots'%20union-negotiated%20pay%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20recover%20from%20its%20second%20bankruptcy%20filing%20in%20under%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20needs%20to%20save%20%24100%20million%20a%20year%20on%20its%20collective%20bargaining%20agreement%20with%20pilots%2C%20Chief%20Operating%20Officer%20John%20Bendoraitis%20told%20the%20pilots'%20union%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20letter%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Spirit%20%26quot%3Bmust%20achieve%20significant%20cost%20savings%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bsecure%20the%20company's%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20challenges%20we%20face%2C%20time%20is%20of%20the%20essence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20proposed%20daily%20meetings%20with%20the%20Air%20Line%20Pilots%20Association%2C%20or%20ALPA%2C%20starting%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20two%20sides%20can't%20reach%20a%20deal%20by%20October%201%2C%20Spirit%20could%20ask%20the%20courts%20to%20change%20or%20reject%20the%20union%20contract%2C%20under%20a%20section%20of%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b837225d-65af-4790-9706-0152f274c686%5C%22%3EHow%20much%20are%20Spirit%20pilots%20paid%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpilot-salary-low-cost-airlines-frontier-allegiant-spirit-union-contracts-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAirline%20pilots'%20pay%3C%2Fa%3E%20varies%20depending%20on%20seniority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20contract%2C%20agreed%20in%202023%2C%20means%20first%20officers%20in%20their%20first%20year%20at%20Spirit%20make%20%2497.15%20an%20hour%2C%20while%20captains%20who%20have%20been%20there%20at%20least%2012%20years%20are%20paid%20%24312%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20minimum%20monthly%20guarantee%20of%2072%20hours%2C%20that%20translates%20to%20annual%20salaries%20between%20roughly%20%2484%2C000%20and%20%24270%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20around%203%2C000%20pilots%2C%20Spirit's%20proposed%20cuts%20suggest%20they%20could%20face%20salary%20cuts%20of%20about%20%2430%2C000%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20value%20of%20seniority%20means%20long-serving%20employees%20could%20face%20a%20pay%20cut%20if%20they%20moved%20to%20another%20airline.%20Spirit%20offers%20the%20highest%20salaries%20of%20US%20budget%20carriers%2C%20although%20Delta%2C%20United%2C%20and%20American%20pay%20starting%20first%20officers%20over%20%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee0fc262-905e-45e4-92fc-dc28c5c6dd71%5C%22%3EThe%20union's%20response%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Ryan%20Muller%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Spirit%20ALPA%20union's%20master%20executive%20council%2C%20wrote%20to%20members%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20launched%20a%20survey%20to%20gather%20their%20thoughts%20on%20the%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20past%20bankruptcy%20proceedings%20show%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20advantage%20to%20reaching%20a%20consensual%20agreement%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20company%2C%20rather%20than%20letting%20the%20bankruptcy%20court%20impose%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20also%20prompted%20Spirit's%20flight%20attendants'%20union%20to%20write%20to%20its%20members%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20airline%20hadn't%20indicated%20it%20wanted%20to%20change%20its%20CBA%2C%20the%20union%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bprepared%20for%20next%20steps%20management%20may%20take.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgain%2C%20this%20bankruptcy%20will%20be%20much%20more%20difficult%20than%20the%20last%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspirit-airlines-financial-bankruptcy-budget-flights-more-expensive-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpirit%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%3C%2F