22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228364%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Vibranium%20Labs%20founding%20team%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cab5e1183847aa39d6ec50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226051%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Vibranium%20Labs%20founding%20team.%3Cp%3EVibranium%20Labs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVibranium%20Labs%20raised%20%244.6%20million%20to%20for%20AI%20agents%20that%20run%2024%2F7%20to%20spot%20IT%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup%20says%20it's%20gaining%20traction%20due%20to%20flaws%20in%20applications%20built%20with%20vibe%20coding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBI%20got%20an%20exclusive%20look%20at%20the%2015-slide%20pitch%20deck%20that%20Vibranium%20Labs%20used%20to%20secure%20the%20funding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20startup%20that's%20built%20AI%20agents%20to%20monitor%20and%20fix%20IT%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20caused%20by%20bad%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-ai-silicon-valley-andrej-karpathy-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evibe%20coding%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20has%20raised%20%244.6%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York-based%20Vibranium%20Labs%20has%20built%20tech%20called%20%26quot%3BVibe%20AI%26quot%3B%20to%20proactively%20monitor%2C%20triage%2C%20and%20resolve%20IT%20incidents%20and%20outages.%20The%20AI%20agent%20plugs%20into%20a%20company's%20existing%20incident%20response%20software%20and%20runs%2024%2F7.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20was%20founded%20by%20Tim%20Hwang%2C%20Sang%20Lee%2C%20Charles%20Kim%2C%20and%20Tanny%20Kang%2C%20who%20collectively%20have%20worked%20at%20a%20number%20of%20tech%20companies%2C%20including%20Google%2C%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20and%20Fiscal%20Note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20aims%20to%20address%20what%20Hwang%20described%20to%20Business%20Insider%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20biggest%20fear%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20for%20software%20engineers%3A%20getting%20a%20call%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20to%20say%20an%20app%20or%20software%20product%20is%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20our%20own%20personal%20issues%20where%20we%20were%20waking%20up%20at%202%20a.m.%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20getting%20pinged%20by%20an%20alert%20saying%20that%20some%20service%20or%20some%20API%20is%20down%20and%20degraded%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Sang%2C%20the%20startup's%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup's%20founders%20say%20its%20technology%20could%20help%20IT%20professionals%20during%20major%20incidents%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-you-need-know-crowdstrike-it-outage-airlines-disruption-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECrowdStrike%20outage%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%20that%20crashed%20millions%20of%20computers%20globally.%20Vibranium%20Labs%20is%20selling%20its%20tech%20on%20a%20per-usage%20model%20and%20targeting%20customers%20in%20industries%20including%20finance%2C%20healthcare%2C%20defense%2C%20retail%2C%20and%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHwang%20and%20Lee%20see%20an%20opportunity%20for%20their%20startup's%20technology%20to%20gain%20traction%20as%20more%20companies%20use%20vibe%20coding%20to%20build%20applications.%20Developers%20who%20are%20using%20text%20prompts%20to%20create%20software%20might%20overlook%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-limits-use-cases-software-companies-airtable-redis-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epotential%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20they%20are%20not%20writing%20the%20code%20manually%2C%20they%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20VCs%20that%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20into%20vibe%20coding%20or%20coding%20assistant%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hwang.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20was%20like%20the%20logical%20next%20step.%20These%20applications%20are%20definitely%20going%20to%20break.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalibrate%20Ventures%20and%20Mirae%20Asset%20led%20Vibranium%20Labs'%20funding%20round%2C%20which%20also%20attracted%20investments%20from%20a16z%2C%20Franklin%20Templeton%2C%20Plug%20and%20Play%2C%20Gaingels%2C%20Wildcard%20Capital%2C%20FalconX%2C%20and%20DCG.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20closed%20their%20seed%20round%20in%20about%20%26quot%3Bsix%20to%20eight%20weeks%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20the%20high%20VC%20interest%20in%20AI%20and%20vibe%20coding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20plan%20to%20use%20the%20fresh%20capital%20to%20accelerate%20product%20innovation%20and%20increase%20the%20size%20of%20the%20startup's%20engineering%20and%20go-to-market%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHere's%20an%20exclusive%20look%20at%20the%20pitch%20deck%20that%20Vibranium%20Labs%20used%20to%20raise%20its%20%244.6%20million%20seed%20round.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221912%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vibranium%20Labs%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cb238d57d362d375e85f26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EVibranium%20Labs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vibranium%20Labs%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cb2666f9db348adc0bae91%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221076%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EVibranium%20Labs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221912%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vibranium%20Labs%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cb26ecf9db348adc0baea0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221078%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EVibranium%20Labs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221916%