ven%20basic%20things%20like%20going%20out%20to%20eat%20or%20getting%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I'm%20cooking%20at%20home%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20before%20I%20was%20married.%20A%20carton%20of%20eggs%20and%20bacon%20will%20last%20me%20and%20my%20kids%20a%20week%2C%20whereas%20even%20fast%20food%20is%20not%20cheap.%20We%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20free%20activities%20now%2C%20like%20going%20to%20parks%20where%20they%20can%20play%20with%20other%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20still%20hear%20it%20from%20them.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvp-product-looking-for-job-over-year-impact-kids-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThey%20notice%20the%20change%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BDad%2C%20why%20aren't%20we%20doing%20this%3F%20Dad%2C%20why%20can't%20we%20go%20here%3F%26quot%3B%20I'm%20honest%20with%20them%20and%20I%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BDad%20doesn't%20make%20enough%20money%20right%20now%20to%20be%20able%20to%20spend%20%24300%20at%20an%20amusement%20park.%20Dad%20doesn't%20have%20the%20%2460%20extra%20to%20buy%20you%20a%20Labubu.%20That's%20why%20you%20got%20the%20one%20from%20the%20gas%20station%20that%20apparently%20is%20not%20real.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20breaks%20my%20heart%20the%20most%20is%20that%20if%20I%20were%20single%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20care.%20I%20can%20eat%20ramen%20noodles%20and%20not%20go%20out%20forever%20if%20I%20have%20to.%20But%20I%20have%20two%20daughters%20that%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20deprive%20of%20the%20things%20I%20was%20deprived%20of%20as%20a%20child%20growing%20up%20in%20Ukraine.%20We%20came%20here%20to%20give%20our%20kids%20a%20better%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20job%3F%20We%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaaltchek%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem